Why This Is Powerful

Because most human friction comes from representation mismatch.

People understand things differently:
	•	engineers → code
	•	scientists → math
	•	managers → diagrams
	•	storytellers → narrative
	•	AI systems → tokens and structure

If you can move the same idea between these layers, you remove huge amounts of friction.

